    "Continuous regression is the omitted baseline analytic method category.",
    "Overall patterns show null effects for most potential study moderators.",
    "These null findings suggest that variation in research and analytical methodology, data structure and scope, self-selection, and study quality typically suspected of biasing private schooling effects do not moderate the civic effects of private schooling observed in this meta-analysis.",
